{"tid":334361,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［優生倫］你班毒撚唔好再問點解自己會溝唔到女？","createTime":"2017-07-24T15:21:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T12:35:33.000Z","uid":69215,"like":18,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d2122e2544a7b5c0b63939376cbf084aa6f225fc","tid":334361,"uid":69215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:21:02.000Z","msg":"事實就係社會既演變係時候要淘汰我地呢班劣等基因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，當大家呻冇女既時候不妨望下自己既高度同樣貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，呢兩項因素之和就係大家既交配值，當然實會有巴打反駁話你有錢有乜女你屌唔撚到，所有女人都係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n但事實係越靚既人智商就越高，而呢班人冇論讀書到將來搵錢都會比班樣衰既叻，呢個就正正解釋到點解d女鐘意靚仔，而d仔就想屌死d靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，因為生出黎既細路基因較好競爭力較高（呢點可以係其他動物身上觀察得到，好似𤠣呢種動物最強最大隻既有，就有優先交配權，目的就係生d基因較好同較大隻既後代）。<br />\n<br />\n而家香港正正就係經歷緊呢個過程，大家出街唔難發現而家後生既一輩靚仔靚女既數量越黎越多，而班00後亦越黎越高平均有成175，相反睇下班廢老廢中多數矮過170<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n社會趨向精英制係必然既事實，垃圾就係要有垃圾既樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，冇交配既權利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：170 好撚樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f096c6ce1df3719d1469b630942b573e184f4f","tid":334361,"uid":61282,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:23:17.000Z","msg":"乜撚野越靚智商越高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7634bce32086f7557b92ad200459f4a58d4a597","tid":334361,"uid":104481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:24:10.000Z","msg":"震驚十三億人口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a7447b3dab990628e59be59d5e7a1a6d7a5448","tid":334361,"uid":69215,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:26:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜撚野越靚智商越高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nLSE研究員金澤（Satoshi Kanazawa）說﹕「英美兩地研究結果同樣指出，身體的吸引力與一般智力（general intelligence）兩者有明顯正面關聯，這種關聯在男性間比女性強烈。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkej.com/node/61721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkej.com%2Fnode%2F61721&d=axfG9w7FiuduG36e9geNTr%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=d4b7c0cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkej.com/node/61721</a>"},{"pid":"2ce075fc0e86e0a124a1bd3e0a75f53c0e318ff1","tid":334361,"uid":61954,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:28:32.000Z","msg":"論字都打錯<br />\n就知你有幾蠢啦"},{"pid":"be3df3370ba1061300cc09ccc5262e557663a8a0","tid":334361,"uid":17813,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:30:27.000Z","msg":"生物學嚟講動物從來都係鍾意強者同靚嘢"},{"pid":"df39abd42950ce16de73e4be9599e5e014b56eee","tid":334361,"uid":69215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:30:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>論字都打錯<br />\n就知你有幾蠢啦</blockquote><br />\n係wo 自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  理科撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大學讀垃圾工程，太耐冇寫文，有d字唔記得左點寫。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67ab90a7e6fafba3d3a6312585584dd63d9e1de6","tid":334361,"uid":29783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:34:21.000Z","msg":"我反而有其他睇法一個社會架構唔可能全部係聰明人，一定要有一班蠢人存在。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以班樣衰既可以同班樣衰既一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7e19260b463780c1378b51ba995955aa75b53c6","tid":334361,"uid":32765,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:36:24.000Z","msg":"真正既聰明人係會盡力確保蠢人既生存空間，而令自己既智力成為特別同珍貴既存在而提升自己既優勢。<br />\n成日提及優生論果班只係自以為聰明過人既蠢人。"},{"pid":"42184b462cb26de75c09d147fdfe676bd8fe6179","tid":334361,"uid":29783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T15:36:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我反而有其他睇法一個社會架構唔可能全部係聰明人，一定要有一班蠢人存在。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以班樣衰既可以同班樣衰既一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你諗下一個社會如果個個一樣咁撚醒會點撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cd13db5ef6c25639a2581a301be2c2988591ae2","tid":334361,"uid":77205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T16:38:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>乜撚野越靚智商越高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nLSE研